飓风伊莎贝尔给北卡罗莱纳州到[[新英格兰|新英格兰]]，甚至向西远至西弗吉尼亚州的广大地区带去了狂风，同时由于之前的降雨导致土壤湿润，狂风行进路径上刮倒了许多树木和电线杆，一度导致600万用户失去电力供应。弗吉尼亚州沿海部分地区，特别是汉普顿锚地以及北卡罗莱纳州东北部断[[电|电]]时间接近一个月。巨浪和强大的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]席卷了沿海地区，北卡罗莱纳州东部和弗吉尼亚州东南部区域都报告因狂风和风暴潮遭受了严重的损失。伊莎贝尔给沿途地区一共造成了36亿美元（2003年美元，相当于{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|3600000000|2003}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元）的经济损失，还有51人遇难，其中有16人是直接因这场风暴而丧生<ref name="assess">{{cite web|author=United States Department of Commerce |year=2004 |title=Service Assessment of Hurricane Isabel |publisher=NOAA |accessdate=2014-02-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203002845/http://www.weather.gov/os/assessments/pdfs/isabel.pdf |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2013-12-03 |url=http://www.weather.gov/os/assessments/pdfs/isabel.pdf |format=PDF }}</ref>。

宾夕法尼亚州、西弗吉尼亚州、马里兰州、新泽西州和特拉华州政府都宣传该州进入紧急状态<ref name="scotsman" />。伊莎贝尔是继1999年9月的[[飓风弗洛伊德|飓风弗洛伊德]]（{{lang|en|Floyd}}）以来第一个对[[中大西洋各州|中大西洋各州]]和[[上南方|上南方]]构成威胁的大型飓风，其造成的损失主要来自[[洪灾|洪灾]]，弗吉尼亚州部分地区的情况是继1972年的[[飓风艾格尼丝|飓风艾格尼丝]]（{{lang|en|Agnes}}）以来最惨重的。超过6000万人受到了一定程度的影响，这个数字与飓风弗洛伊德接近，但比其它任何一场近期发生的飓风都要多<ref name="ncdcisfl">{{cite web |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Climate of 2003- Comparison of Hurricanes Floyd, Hugo and Isabel |accessdate=2014-02-07 |archivedate=2012-02-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120214074913/http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2003/fl-hu-is-comp.html |deadurl=no |url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2003/fl-hu-is-comp.html}}</ref>。

=== 加勒比地区和美国东南部 ===
[[大安的列斯群岛|大安的列斯群岛]]北部海岸受到了强大的海浪冲击，[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]也遭遇了强烈的涌浪。巴哈马的特殊地址位置曾保护[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]东南沿海免受大部分大西洋飓风引起的强烈涌浪袭击，然而，伊莎贝尔的力道、前进速度和行进路线相结合，产生的涌浪穿过普罗维登斯海峡，冲到了佛罗里达州东南部长约16公里的狭窄海岸线上，[[德拉海滩|德拉海滩]]出现了高达4.3米的巨浪<ref name="iswav" />。[[博因顿海滩_(佛罗里达州)|博因顿海滩]]有一艘船因涌浪而倾覆，船上两名乘客受伤，[[朱诺海滩_(佛罗里达州)|朱诺海滩]]附近有一位游泳者向救生员请求救援。[[棕櫚灘縣|棕櫚灘縣]]报告出现了轻度海岸浸蚀<ref name="flncdc">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |accessdate=2014-02-08 | archivedate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | format = PDF |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Florida}}</ref>。该州北部的[[弗拉格勒海滩_(佛罗里达州)|弗拉格勒海滩]]海浪达到4.5米高，导致当地码头因受损而关闭<ref name="flncdc2">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |accessdate=2014-02-08 | archivedate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | format = PDF |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Florida (2)}}</ref>。[[拿骚县_(佛罗里达州)|拿骚县]]有一人在无人看守的海滩上冲浪，结果因遇上伊莎贝尔产生的离岸流而丧生，另外还有六人因遭遇离岸流而求救<ref name="flncdc3">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |accessdate=2014-02-08 | archivedate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | format = PDF |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Florida (3)}}</ref>。之后海浪继续增大，这些海滩也予以关闭<ref name="flncdc4">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |accessdate=2014-02-08 | archivedate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | format = PDF |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Florida (4)}}</ref>。

飓风的外围[[雨带|雨带]]给南卡罗莱纳州东北部的[[默特尔比奇_(南卡罗来纳州)|默特尔比奇]]带去了时速72公里的大风，不过降雨量不多，最高的[[洛里斯_(南卡罗来纳州)|洛里斯]]也只有34[[毫米|毫米]]<ref name="wilnws">{{cite web |author=Wilmington, North Carolina National Weather Service |year=2003 |title=Hurricane Isabel in South Carolina |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130609032655/http://www.erh.noaa.gov/ilm/archive/09-18-03/index.shtml |accessdate=2014-02-07 |url=http://www.erh.noaa.gov/ilm/archive/09-18-03/index.shtml |archivedate=2013-06-09 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

=== 北卡罗莱纳州 ===
[[File:Hurricane_Isabel_flood_water.jpg|thumb]][[兰利空军基地|兰利空军基地]]因飓风伊莎贝尔而出现的洪水]]
{{main|飓风伊莎贝尔对北卡罗莱纳州的影响}}
伊莎贝尔给北卡罗莱纳州东部造成了中到重度的损失，总额达到4.5亿美元（2003年美元，相当于{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|450000000|2003}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元）<ref name="tcr" />。受灾最为严重的是[[戴尔县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|戴尔县]]，狂风和风暴潮引发的洪水令成千上万的房屋受损<ref name="ncncdc">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for North Carolina |accessdate=2014-02-08 | archivedate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | format = PDF}}</ref>。风暴潮还在哈特拉斯岛上冲出了一个宽600米的水湾，这里之后也被非正式地称为伊莎贝尔水湾，哈特拉斯的陆路交通也因此中断了两个月之久<ref name="outban">{{cite web |author=Fred Hurteau |year=2003 |title=The Dynamic Landscape of the Outer Banks |publisher=Outer Banks Guidebook |accessdate=2012-03-18 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2012-03-18 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120318075258/http://outerbanksguidebook.com/dynamic.htm |url=http://www.outerbanksguidebook.com/dynamic.htm}}</ref>。狂风在全州吹倒了成百上千的树木和电线杆，致使70万居民家中停电，不过大部分停电地区在几天后就恢复了电力供应<ref name="ncncdc" />。飓风还在该州直接造成一人死亡，间接导致两人丧生<ref name="isab">{{cite web |author=Sunbelt Rentals |year=2003 |title=Hurricane Isabel Aftermath |accessdate=2008-04-09 |url=http://www.sunbeltrentals.com/news/HurricaneIsabelAftermath.pdf |format=PDF |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080409100013/http://www.sunbeltrentals.com/news/HurricaneIsabelAftermath.pdf |archivedate=2008-04-09}}</ref>。

=== 弗吉尼亚州 ===
{{main|飓风伊莎贝尔对弗吉尼亚州的影响}}
弗吉尼亚州东南部大部分地区都受到了风暴潮的冲击，其中[[里士满_(维吉尼亚州)|里士满]][[詹姆斯河|詹姆斯河]]沿岸估计达到最高的2.7米，这些潮水导致河流沿岸的民房严重受损<ref name="assess" />，特别是在詹姆斯河流域中游沿岸<ref name="rain">{{cite web |author=David Roth |year=2005 |title=Rainfall Summary for Hurricane Isabel |publisher=Hydrometeorological Prediction Center |accessdate=2014-02-07 |archivedate=2013-12-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131206140210/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/isabel2003.html |url=http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/isabel2003.html}}</ref>。强烈的风暴潮突破了该州中城隧道的防洪闸，当时工人试图关闭防洪闸，但近17万[[立方米|立方米]]的洪水仅用40[[分钟|分钟]]就完全淹没了隧道，不过所有工人都勉强逃出生天<ref name="isab" />。

风暴对电网的破坏结合洪水的影响，导致当地包括[[奥多明尼昂大学|奥多明尼昂大学]]、[[诺福克州立大学|诺福克州立大学]]在内的多所主要学府关闭了近一周。更内陆的地区报告降下暴雨，其中最高的上谢拉顿达513毫米<ref name="rain" />，导致了损失和严重的洪灾。飓风带来的狂风摧毁上千幢房屋，还有九千多套受损<ref name="ncdc1">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Virginia |accessdate=2014-02-08 | archivedate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | format = PDF}}</ref>，全州遭受的经济损失约为18.5亿美元（2003年美元，相当于{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|1850000000|2003}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元），创下该州史上热带气旋新纪录<ref name="assess" />。伊莎贝尔致使该州32人遇难，其中十人属直接导致，22人间接引起<ref name="tcr" />。

=== 中大西洋各州 ===
[[File:Isabel_2003_rainfall.gif|thumb]]
{{main|飓风伊莎贝尔对特拉华州的影响|飓风伊莎贝尔对马里兰州和哥伦比亚特区的影响}}
马里兰州和哥伦比亚特区约有124万人失去电力供应。伊莎贝尔产生的风暴潮对这些地区造成了最严重的影响，淹没了沿海地区，并导致严重的海岸侵蚀。马里兰州东部有成百上千的建筑物因风暴潮和潮汐引发的洪水而受损甚至完全被摧毁。[[多切斯特县_(马里兰州)|多切斯特县]]和[[萨默塞特县_(马里兰州)|萨默塞特县]]南部，以及[[安妮女王县|安妮女王县]]的[[肯特岛|肯特岛]]（{{lang|en|Kent Island}}）发生了最为严重的洪灾。马里兰州中部也有成千上万套房屋受到影响，[[巴尔的摩|巴尔的摩]]和[[安那波利斯|安那波利斯]]报告因风暴潮而出现了严重的洪灾。哥伦比亚特区持续遭受了中等程度的损失，主要是由狂风引起。整个马里兰州和哥伦比亚特区的经济损失共达到约9.45亿美元（2003年美元，相当于{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|945000000|2003}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元），还有一人直接因风暴引发的洪水而遇难<ref name="esncdc">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Eastern Maryland |accessdate=2014-02-08 | archivedate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | format = PDF}}</ref><ref name="midncdc">{{cite report |author=NCDC |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Central Maryland |accessdate=2014-02-08 | archivedate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | format = PDF}}</ref><ref name="wmdncdc">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Western Maryland |accessdate=2014-02-08 | archivedate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | format = PDF}}</ref><ref name="dcncdc">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Washington, D.C. |accessdate=2014-02-08 | archivedate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | format = PDF}}</ref>。

[[特拉华州|特拉华州]]在伊莎贝尔来袭几天前刚因[[2003年热带风暴亨利|热带风暴亨利]]的残留引发洪灾，这场飓风又进一步加重了灾情<ref name="drc">{{cite web |author=FEMA |year=2003 |title=Disaster Recovery Centers to Open |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120315134043/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=5178 |archivedate=2012-03-15 |accessdate=2006-12-26 |url=http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=5178 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>。[[刘易斯_(特拉华州)|刘易斯]]出现了时速100公里的狂风<ref name="phil">{{cite web |author=Gorse & Frugis |year=2003 |title=Hurricane Isabel Post Tropical Storm Report |publisher=Mount Holly, New Jersey National Weather Service |accessdate=2014-02-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120205045840/http://www.erh.noaa.gov/er/phi/storms/09192003.txt |deadurl=no |url=http://www.erh.noaa.gov/er/phi/storms/09192003.txt |format=TXT |archivedate=2012-02-05}}</ref>，全州有大量树木和电线杆被刮倒，还吹断了许多树枝<ref name="delncdc">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Delaware |accessdate=2014-02-08 | archivedate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | format = PDF}}</ref>，导致至少15300人家中停电<ref name="isabel1">{{cite web|author=Joint Information Center |year=2003 |title=Sporadic Power Outages Being Reported Across State |publisher=Delaware Emergency Management Agency |accessdate=2014-02-07 |archivedate=2012-02-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120216001048/http://dema.delaware.gov/press_release/Isabel_1.pdf |deadurl=yes |url=http://dema.delaware.gov/press_release/Isabel_1.pdf |format=PDF }}</ref>。强烈的海浪和风暴潮以及内陆地区的径流泛滥导致许多低洼地区被淹<ref name="delncdc" />。飓风伊莎贝尔一共给该州造成了4000万美元（2003年美元，相当于{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|40000000|2003}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元）的经济损失，不过幸运的是全州没有人员丧生<ref name="tcr" />。

=== 美国东北部 ===
[[File:Hurricane_Isabel_(Canada).JPG|thumb]]上空的飓风伊莎贝尔]]
