伊莎贝尔产生的狂风刮倒了新泽西州成百上千的树木和电线杆，导致数十万居民家中停电，有一人被倒下的树木砸死。海岸沿线因汹涌的海浪和中等强度的风暴潮而引发了中到重度的海岸侵蚀，还有一人在海浪中淹死。全州经济损失达到5000万美元（2003年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|50000000|2003}}}}美元）<ref name="tcr" /><ref name="njncdc">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for New Jersey |accessdate=2014-02-08 | archivedate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | format = PDF}}</ref><ref name="beachy">{{cite web |author=New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection |year=2003 |title=Coastal Storm Survey |accessdate=2014-02-07 |archivedate=2012-02-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120212211155/http://www.nj.gov/dep/shoreprotection/StormSurvey09-19-03.pdf |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.nj.gov/dep/shoreprotection/StormSurvey09-19-03.pdf |format=PDF}}</ref>。

飓风伊莎贝尔给宾夕法尼亚州造成了1.6亿美元（2003年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|160000000|2003}}}}美元）的经济损失<ref name="tcr" />。有一人出现了[[一氧化碳|一氧化碳]]中毒，据信是因为他于停电后在通风不畅的地方操作发电机所致<ref name="mono">{{cite news |author=CNN |title=Isabel death toll creeps higher |accessdate=2014-02-07 |archivedate=2005-04-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20050415115634/http://edition.cnn.com/2003/WEATHER/09/22/isabel/index.html |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2003/WEATHER/09/22/isabel/index.html | date=2003-09-22}}</ref>。狂风将树木刮倒并砸在电缆上，数十幢房屋和汽车被树砸伤，还有约140万户居民家中停电<ref name="penncdc">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Southeast Pennsylvania |accessdate=2014-02-08 | archivedate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | format = PDF}}</ref><ref name="cenpendcd">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Central Pennsylvania |accessdate=2014-02-08 | archivedate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | format = PDF}}</ref><ref name="nwscen">{{cite web |author=State College, Pennsylvania National Weather Service |year=2003 |title=Hurricane Isabel: September 2003 |accessdate=2014-02-07 |url=http://www.erh.noaa.gov/ctp/features/2003/isabel.php |archivedate=2012-04-16 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120416025610/http://www.erh.noaa.gov/ctp/features/2003/isabel.php |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

[[纽约州|纽约州]]遭受了9000万美元（2003年美元，相当于{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|90000000|2003}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元）的经济损失<ref name="tcr" />，[[佛蒙特州|佛蒙特州]]也报告了约10万美元（2003年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{formatnum:{{Inflation|US|100000|2003|r=-3}}}}美元）的损失<ref name="verncdc1">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003|title=Event Report for Vermont |accessdate=2014-02-08 | archivedate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | format = PDF}}</ref><ref name="verncdc2">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Vermont (2) |accessdate=2014-02-08 | archivedate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | format = PDF}}</ref><ref name="verncdc3">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Vermont (3) |accessdate=2014-02-08 | archivedate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | format = PDF}}</ref><ref name="verncdc4">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Vermont (4) |accessdate=2014-02-08 | archivedate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | format = PDF}}</ref><ref name="verncdc5">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Vermont (5) |accessdate=2014-02-08 | archivedate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | format = PDF}}</ref><ref name="verncdc6">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Vermont (6) |accessdate=2014-02-08 | archivedate = 2014-02-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140208072341/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-1B3648A1-CEA9-4E12-8838-ADCEA8505069.pdf | format = PDF}}</ref>。全州各处都有树木和电线杆被狂风吹倒，导致局部地区停电。还有两人因伊莎贝尔产生的大浪而遇难<ref name="tcr" />。

=== 其它地区 ===
风暴给西弗吉尼亚州带去了中等程度降水，其中降雨量最高的舒格格罗夫（{{lang|en|Sugar Grove}}）附近达到175毫米<ref name="Mid Atl">{{cite book |author=Roth, David M |author2=Weather Prediction Center |year=2012 |title=Tropical Cyclone Rainfall Point Maxima |chapter=Tropical Cyclone Rainfall in the Mid-Atlantic United States |publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service |accessdate=2014-02-08 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140203171339/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmidatl.html |deadurl=no |archivedate=2014-02-03 |url=http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmidatl.html}}</ref>。降雨引起[[泥石流|泥石流]]和山洪爆发，堵塞了多条道路，还冲跨了两座桥梁。[[波托马克河|波托马克河]]位于斯普林菲尔德（{{lang|en|Springfield}}）附近河段涨至7.5米深，比洪水标准还高2.8米。迈克尔菲尔德（{{lang|en|Michael Field}}）的一处大堤被洪水冲垮，[[米纳勒尔县_(西弗吉尼亚州)|米纳勒尔县]]有一所学校和14个[[地下室|地下室]]被淹。[[杰弗逊县_(西弗吉尼亞州)|杰弗逊县]]有一辆车冲进了洪水中，车上两人向外求救<ref name="ncdc">{{cite report |author=National Climatic Data Center |year=2003 |title=Event Report for Hurricane Isabel |accessdate=2012-01-13 |archivedate=2012-01-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120113003220/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~521900 |url=http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~521900}}</ref>。虽然风暴给该州带去的持续风速不高，但[[马丁斯堡_(西弗吉尼亚州)|马丁斯堡]]的阵风时速还是达到了74公里。由于地面已被雨水和洪水浸湿，阵风扳倒了成千上万的树木和电线杆，并且倒在住房和道路上造成了进一步损失<ref name="ncdc" />。全州有约140万居民家中断电<ref name="assess" />，经济损失达到2000万美元（2003年美元，相当于{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|20000000|2003}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元），不过幸运的是没有出现人员死亡的报道<ref name="tcr" />，只有三人因飓风受伤<ref name="ncdc" />。

[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]]东部普降小到中雨，局部地区报告的降雨量超过75毫米<ref name="rain" />。伊莎贝尔的湿气还给[[密歇根州|密歇根州]]东部带去了降水，其中最高的[[芒特克莱门斯|芒特克莱门斯]]（{{lang|en|Mount Clemens}}）达到39毫米。此外根据[[气象雷达|多普勒气象雷达]]的数据，估计[[圣克莱尔县_(密歇根州)|圣克莱尔县]]的降雨量达到64毫米。不过这两个州都没有出现因伊莎贝尔导致经济损失或人员伤亡的报道<ref name="Michigan">{{cite web |author=Detroit National Weather Service |year=2003 |title=Remnants of Isabel Bring Rainfall to Southeast Michigan Friday Morning |accessdate=2014-02-08 |archivedate=2012-10-18 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018181550/http://www.crh.noaa.gov/dtx/isabel2003.php |url=http://www.crh.noaa.gov/dtx/isabel2003.php}}</ref>。

伊莎贝尔产生的涌浪给[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]的大西洋沿岸带去了中等高度海浪，其中又以[[缅因湾|缅因湾]]最为典型<ref name="chc918" />，安大略湖也因风暴产生大浪，其西半部的浪高达到4米。海浪超过了[[哈密尔顿_(安大略)|哈密尔顿]]的海堤喷酒到沿海街道上<ref name="summary" />。风暴带去的最高降雨量为59毫米，引发了轻度洪水和交通事故，有一人在事故中丧生。约有27000人家中停电，其中大部分居住在[[多伦多|多伦多]]附近<ref>{{cite report |publisher=Environment Canada |date=2010-09-14 |title=2003-Isabel |accessdate=2014-02-08 |archivedate=2013-10-05 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131005233613/http://www.ec.gc.ca/hurricane/default.asp?lang=En&n=9BE4D4C2-1 |url=http://www.ec.gc.ca/Hurricane/default.asp?lang=En&n=9BE4D4C2-1}}</ref>。伊莎贝尔和加拿大东部上空的一个[[高气压|高压系统]]之间强烈的压力梯度在整个安大略湖和伊利湖区域产生了强烈的东风<ref name="summary" />。安大略湖的一个[[浮标|浮标]]记录到时速78公里的最高阵风风速<ref name="chc920">{{cite web|author=Szeto and LaFortune |year=2003 |title=Hurricane Isabel Information Statement on September 20, 2003 |publisher=Canadian Hurricane Center |accessdate=2014-02-08 |archivedate=十一月 20, 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131120065808/http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20030920070900.Isabel.info.txt.en |url=http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20030920070900.Isabel.info.txt.en }}</ref>，安大略[[科尔本港|科尔本港]]（{{lang|en|Port Colborne}}）的阵风风速更达到了每小时81公里<ref name="tcr" />。

== 余波 ==
[[File:Hatteras_Island_damage_by_Hurricane_Isabel.jpg|thumb]]
飓风过去约一星期后，[[美国总统|美国总统]][[乔治·沃克·布什|乔治·沃克·布什]]宣布北卡罗莱纳州的36个县，弗吉尼亚州的77个县和自治市，整个马里兰州和特拉华州，以及西弗吉尼亚州的[[西弗吉尼亚州行政区划|6个县]]为灾区。这些地区因此可以获得联邦基金的援助重建家园<ref name="assess" />。伊莎贝尔过去约4个月后，动用的灾难援助金额达到约5.16亿美元（2003年美元，相当于{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|516000000|2003}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元），其中大部分用在北卡罗莱纳州和弗吉尼亚州。超过16.6万居民申请了单独援助，一共获得了约1.17亿美元（2003年美元，相当于{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|117000000|2003}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元）以修建临时房屋并对住房加以修补。约5万名店主申请了小型企业管理局贷款，共计获得了约1.78亿美元（2003年美元，相当于{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|178000000|2003}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元）。约4万人访问了地方灾难恢复中心，这里旨在向人们提供飓风过后的相关附加信息<ref name="ncfema">{{cite web |author=FEMA |year=2003 |title=State/Federal Disaster Aid Tops $155 Million in North Carolina |accessdate=2007-02-13 |archivedate=2012-02-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120211080517/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=9029 |url=http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=9029}}</ref><ref name="vafema">{{cite web |author=FEMA |year=2004 |title=Commonwealth of Virginia Receives Nearly $257 Million In Disaster Assistance |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120211081225/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=10604 |accessdate=2012-02-11 |url=http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=10604 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2012-02-11}}</ref><ref name="mdfema">{{cite web |author=FEMA |year=2003 |title=Maryland Disaster Aid Nearing $100 Million |accessdate=2012-03-15 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120315134500/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=9314 |archivedate=2012-03-15 |url=http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=9314 |deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name="defema">{{cite web |deadurl=yes |author=FEMA |year=2003 |title=Disaster Victims in Delaware Receive Over $3.5 Million In Assistance So Far |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120205020555/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=7748 |accessdate=2012-02-05 |url=http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=7748 |archivedate=2012-02-05}}</ref><ref name="pafema">{{cite web |author=FEMA |year=2003 |title=Disaster Aid in Pennsylvania Surpasses Half Million Dollars |accessdate=2012-02-05 |url=http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6792 |archivedate=2012-02-05 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120205020615/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6792 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

北卡罗莱纳州的哈特拉斯因伊莎贝尔水湾的形成而导致成百上千的居民被困<ref name="isab" />。由于飓风导致道路受损，外滩群岛上连续两个星期只允许当地居民进入及居留。游客终于获许进入后，许多人大胆地前往查看新形成的水湾，这里距最近的道路都需要步行1.6公里<ref name="outban" />。起初曾考虑修筑桥梁或是增加渡轮系统来作为伊莎贝尔水湾交通问题的长期解决方案，不过最终还是决定使用沙子对水湾进行填充。沿海地质学家反对这一填充方案，他们表示外滩群岛的发展都依赖于飓风形成的水湾<ref name="natgeo">{{cite web |author=John Roach |year=2003 |title=Shoring Up N. Carolina Islands: A Losing Battle? |publisher=National Geographic News |accessdate=2014-02-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120309153708/http://news.nationalgeographic.com/news/2003/11/1110_031110_outerbanks.html |deadurl=no |url=http://news.nationalgeographic.com/news/2003/11/1110_031110_outerbanks.html |archivedate= 2012-03-09}}</ref>。疏浚工程于飓风袭击后约一个月的10月17日开始。[[美国地质调查局|美国地质调查局]]使用的沙子主要来自于哈特拉斯岛西南部的轮渡海峡，这一方面是为了尽可能减少对沉水植物的影响，同时也是为了疏通飓风期间被填满的海峡<ref name="fem3">{{cite web |author=Federal Emergency Management Agency |year=2003 |title=Dredging Operations Begin |accessdate=2006-12-16 |url=http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6315 |archivedate=2010-06-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100608031004/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6315 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>。飓风袭击约两个月后的11月22日，[[北卡罗莱纳州12号高速公路|北卡罗莱纳州12号高速公路]]和哈特拉斯岛都重新向公众开放。当天重新开放的还有哈特拉斯岛到奥克拉科克岛的轮渡服务<ref name="outban" />。

西弗吉尼亚州停电的地区在一星期内相继恢复<ref name="iser3">
{{cite web |author=United States Department of Energy |year=2003 |title=Hurricane Isabel Situation Report: September 25, 2003 |accessdate=2007-02-07 |archivedate=2013-03-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130302233505/https://www.oe.netl.doe.gov/docs/isabel/hurrisabel_sitrep_092503_0900.pdf |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.oe.netl.doe.gov/docs/isabel/hurrisabel_sitrep_092503_0900.pdf }}
</ref>。加拿大各地的电力工人对从马里兰州到北卡罗莱纳州的多家受到严重影响的供电公司提供协助<ref name="fact">{{cite web |author=Constellation Energy |year=2003 |title=The Facts: Hurricane Isabel and BGE |accessdate=2009-03-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090319215704/http://www.constellation.com/vcmfiles/Constellation/Files/factsheet_isabel.pdf |url=http://www.constellation.com/vcmfiles/Constellation/Files/factsheet_isabel.pdf |archivedate=2009-03-19}}</ref>。[[魁北克电力公司|魁北克电力公司]]派出25支队伍前往纽约市周边地区协助恢复供电<ref name="cbcis">{{cite news |author=CBC News |title=Isabel to bring heavy winds to eastern Ontario |accessdate=2014-02-08 |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/ottawa/isabel-to-bring-heavy-winds-to-eastern-ontario-1.410383 | date=2003-09-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140208034228/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/ottawa/isabel-to-bring-heavy-winds-to-eastern-ontario-1.410383 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2014-02-08}}</ref>。

由于这场飓风造成了大范围的严重财产损失并造成大量人员伤亡，其名称“伊莎贝尔”也在2003年飓风季后退役，不会再在将来的大西洋热带气旋中使用。用来替换的新名称是“{{lang|en|Ida}}”（音译“艾达”），这个名称在[[2009年大西洋飓风季|2009年大西洋飓风季]]中[[飓风艾达|首度使用]]<ref name="wmo1">{{cite web |author=World Meteorological Organization |year=2004 |title=Final Report of the 2003 Hurricane Season |accessdate=2014-02-08 |archivedate=2013-11-04 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131104140940/http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/www/tcp/documents/HC26-English.pdf |url=http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/www/tcp/documents/HC26-English.pdf |format=PDF |deadurl=no}}</ref>。[[世界气象组织|世界气象组织]]还曾考虑用“{{lang|en|Ina}}”（音译“伊娜”）和“{{lang|en|Ivy}}”（音译“艾维”）来进行替换<ref name="wmo2">{{cite report | author = World Meteorological Organization | year = 2004 | title = Replacement Names for 2003 Atlantic Hurricanes (Fabian, Isabel, and Juan) and 2002 Hurricane Lili}}</ref>。

